{"tid":2100911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"首家「量子通訊」概念股在中國科創板上市，首日一度飆升8倍！","createTime":"2020-07-09T11:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T15:11:14.000Z","uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e51b73a79d70cabce212d881d65882aeac0c98a","tid":2100911,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"香港炒緊阿里巴巴的時候，中國已經炒緊「量子通訊」，領先全球100年！<br />\n<br />\n7月9日，中國量子通信領域首家A股上市企業誕生，國盾量子在科創板上市。國盾量子開盤即出現大幅拉升，盤中一度上漲達881%，創下科創板公司首日漲幅紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n2009年國盾量子在合肥成立，由中科院院士潘建偉、中國科學技術大學研究員彭承誌等創辦。主要從事量子保密通信產品的研發、生產、銷售及技術服務等，為各類光纖量子保密通信網絡以及&ldquo;星地一體&rdquo;廣域量子保密通信地面站的建設提供軟硬件產品。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">2019年，國盾量子營業收入2.58億元，淨利潤為5353萬元，已經實現了盈利。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/406619279_115362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F406619279_115362&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=8a79e973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/406619279_115362</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1281187570399887364?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1281187570399887364%3Fs%3D20&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=ae975d19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1281187570399887364%3Fs%3D20&h=7219ccc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1281187570399887364?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTyuR4gnpUqs&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=32d1d4fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs</a>"},{"pid":"11a4a9caf46437b894152e7f65664b04819ce815","tid":2100911,"uid":39419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re